      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL ABOUT SADIE (1) has been in the money a lot of late and went close again last time over 2200m at this track, finishing third and 9 metres from the winner. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Tackles a similar assignment and she can grab that well-deserved win. WINSUM BELLA (2) made it two on the trot last start when she got the cash by 3.5 metres over 1680m here. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. This doesn't look as hard so she is in the right race to register the hat-trick. CHEYS ANGEL (5) disappointed last time when ninth over 2200m at this circuit. Is better than recent efforts suggest and can bounce back. STANTON BREAK (4) has been about the mark of late and must be respected, the latest offering a sound second at this course over 1680m. One for the multiples.",
